name: Experiment Or Die #72
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. I've been hosting Twitter spaces now for a few weeks and the upcoming episode is featuring an amazing artist named Steven Daily. After reviewing his work I immediately noticed that he paints skulls ALOT and I got inspired to create todays design in his honor. The main image is a photo of a Powell Peralta ripper mural that I painted here in Atlanta with my trademark layering and color pops! Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
